list.definition:
base_table = from(bucket: "hsebucket")
  |> range(start: -1d)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "libiotrace_control")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => contains(value: r["jobname"], set: ${jobname:json}))
  |> filter(fn: (r) => contains(value: r["hostname"], set: ${host:json}))
  |> filter(fn: (r) => contains(value: r["processid"], set: ${process:json}))
  |> filter(fn: (r) => contains(value: r["thread"], set: ${thread:json}))
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1ns, fn: last, createEmpty: false)

ip = base_table
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "ip")

port = base_table
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "port")

join(tables: {ip: ip, port: port}, on: ["_time", "jobname", "hostname", "processid", "thread"])
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({
//      ip: r["_value_ip"],
//      port: r["_value_port"],
      address: r["_value_ip"] + ":" + string(v: r["_value_port"])
    })
  )
